A great low-rate way to finance major expenses.
Whether you’re making home improvements, planning to consolidate higher-interest-rate debt,1 or handling other major expenses, a Bank of America® home equity line of credit gives you the flexibility to manage it all.  During the 10-year borrowing period,2 you can access your funds over and over (up to your available credit limit) and use the money when and where you need it.
Additional benefits:



Special discounts3 – Interest rate discounts are available based on how much you withdraw at account opening and whether you set up automatic payments at that time
                    

No costs to apply – No application fees, closing costs or annual fee2

Low interest rates – Rates are typically lower than most credit cards or personal loans

Protection from rising interest rates – Our Fixed-Rate Loan Option2 allows you to convert a portion of your outstanding balance from a variable interest rate to a fixed rate with fixed monthly payments




