Whether you’re making home improvements, planning to consolidate higher-interest-rate debt,1 or handling other major expenses, a Bank of America® home equity line of credit gives you the flexibility to manage it all.  During the 10-year borrowing period,2 you can access your funds over and over (up to your available credit limit) and use the money when and where you need it.
